</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id2070989" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1584662">
<para id="import-auto-id2103213">What is the cost of operating a 3.00-W electric clock for a year if the cost of electricity is $0.0900 per <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mtext>kW</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">⋅</m:mo><m:mn>h</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>?</para></problem></exercise>
